Package se.swedenconnect.opensaml.sweid.saml2.metadata.entitycategory

Interface EntityCategoryRegistry

All Known Implementing Classes:
EntityCategoryRegistryImpl
public interface EntityCategoryRegistry
A registry that handles all "registered" entity categories. It is used to find the definition of an entity category based on its URI.
Author:
Martin Lindström (martin@idsec.se)
